    <tr><td>2</td><td>Open Projects</td><td>Project list opens</td></tr>
    <tr><td>3</td><td>Search for authorized project</td><td>Authorized project visible</td></tr>
    <tr><td>4</td><td>Search for out-of-scope project</td><td>Out-of-scope project hidden or denied</td></tr>
    <tr><td>5</td><td>Open View, Tasks, Status Board, or Reports as relevant</td><td>Visibility remains correctly restricted</td></tr>
